lead_paragraph: Draymond Green emphatically flexed his bulging biceps with big plays on both ends of the floor, and these Golden State Warriors might just be far too strong for the Cleveland Cavaliers.

headline.print_headline: Warriors Whip Cavaliers 110-77 to Take 2-0 NBA Finals Lead
